{"tid":2125093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"豬肚湯加料蝙蝠　餐飲業亂象不絕","createTime":"2020-07-26T02:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T04:44:51.000Z","uid":51665,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"301931ad64dc6d5ac368c7506ed7b9de5fb92cd6","tid":2125093,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20200726/bkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcommentary%2F20200726%2Fbkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=796914bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20200726/bkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html</a><br />\n世界各地的新冠肺炎疫情至今未有受控迹象，內地雖然抗疫成績領先，但好了傷疤忘了痛的死性不改。最先爆發疫情的湖北武漢，餐飲業依然亂象叢生。有當地民眾從食店外賣豬肚湯回家，竟駭然發現是蝙蝠湯，掛羊頭賣狗肉，監管當局卻置若罔聞，一旦病從口入，疫情再起，該當何罪？<br />\n<br />\n武漢陳先生近日在某食店買了一煲豬肚湯回家，連續喝到第三日才發現湯內有一隻完整的蝙蝠，嚇得一家人趕緊去做病毒核酸檢測，幸未驗出病毒。陳先生隨即往食店理論，惟對方卻指自己只是分銷商，熬製工序是生產商的事；生產商則稱熬湯過程費時，若是己方所為，蝙蝠早應被煮爛，反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去，結果成了各有各說，不知該相信誰。<br />\n<br />\n正如當地市場監管部門事後檢查指出，相關食店的衞生及生產環節俱無發現問題，又表示涉事生產商在當地已經營多年，過往檢查亦未發現有甚麼不合規情況，看來欲知真相，惟有去問蝙蝠，那又要市監作甚？好在食店的老闆比較有「人情味」，表示願向客人支付一定精神補償及相關核酸檢測費用，估計事件至此已是最「圓滿」的結局，否則再糾纏下去，食客有無精力奉陪已是疑問，搞不好還會上演事件「反轉」，豈非自找麻煩？<br />\n<br />\n不可不知，武漢市早前爆發奪命新冠肺炎疫情，搞得人心惶惶，病毒源頭就被高度懷疑來自蝙蝠等野生動物，如今更被拿來煲湯，不叫人害怕才怪。莫說是蝙蝠，就算吃到老鼠、蟑螂、蒼蠅也不能容忍，問題更非像非洲豬瘟病死豬肉那樣，強調煮熟吃就沒事了，顧客吃了「加料」食物，一句檢疫正常、身體健康又能代表甚麼？保障餐飲業乃至整個食品行業的安全衞生是民生大事，更是政府不可推卸的責任，不能每次都語焉不詳，不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n民以食為天，食以安為先。可惜內地餐飲業衞生安全問題總是爆完又爆，沒完沒了，民眾更別指望可以食得安心。而且每次發生類似的問題，地方監管部門似乎都已形成了一套嫺熟的應對措施，不是說食肆衞生檢查正常，就是以源頭無法追查搪塞，再來就像江蘇南京江寧區市監人員那樣，在處理高速公路服務區餐廳吃到蛆蟲投訴時，任由餐廳經理當面吃掉蛆蟲毀證，令人瞠目結舌。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，更多的食安問題不是由食客主動檢舉揭發，就是由媒體記者深入虎穴做臥底，探查取證踢爆，所有監管部門都彷彿成了擺設，箇中原由不問可知。想必平時都被打點好了，層層包庇，食安亂象豈能不是層出不窮！<br />\n<br />\n良心店！買豬肚送蝙蝠咁蝕底嘅嘢都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cad0322af86c7ed6c6222f2d6b8b78a67695d0","tid":2125093,"uid":81273,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<br />\n講完自己有冇笑"},{"pid":"f880d0fc387e5ba0442b24b8cea794d381172948","tid":2125093,"uid":291526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29692388244fd17744c51351040bf5764a88e33f","tid":2125093,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"又想翻爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e28afaa89cf35a06f36f0ed69f487d1a504f1a","tid":2125093,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b7cad0322af86c7ed6c6222f2d6b8b78a67695d0","tid":2125093,"uid":81273,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<br />\n講完自己有冇笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"最好笑其實係後面呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">結果成了各有各說，不知該相信誰。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5d17462e6a2037347b6532658d5a316940056a34","tid":2125093,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"實驗室用果D唔係野生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255535bd3e8821482c32fc2e9aadb7af21981736","tid":2125093,"uid":279357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"合乎武漢文化放錯料姐<br />\n啲蝙蝠仔湯係領導飲架"},{"pid":"9448d9f5a4ddfc3a168f0b79394f393ae805b3eb","tid":2125093,"uid":266676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒你識d 咩， 中国文化5千年"},{"pid":"d49310ab60c22a868cc7ef5741df83b5246bc2aa","tid":2125093,"uid":3063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"好閪補嫁<br />\n唔閪識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497de4fcacda06fa707bf6ef47f48e28248eeba6","tid":2125093,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"點解支那人咁鍾情蝙蝠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac566a904ce94ae7649fac7a9aa9acfff6757b9","tid":2125093,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:12:15.000Z","msg":"連續喝到第三日才發現湯內有一隻完整的蝙蝠<br />\n<br />\n一煲湯煲咗咁多日都仲未變？"},{"pid":"8389a9b3f9f258dd3ed2abca5b714c1748b67b1c","tid":2125093,"uid":31463,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b7cad0322af86c7ed6c6222f2d6b8b78a67695d0","tid":2125093,"uid":81273,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<br />\n講完自己有冇笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"咁似黑警講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec69e2651996aaab2b31b58b15692e872a52f45c","tid":2125093,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f880d0fc387e5ba0442b24b8cea794d381172948","tid":2125093,"uid":291526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"睇下連登最近被沉底既重要新聞：<br />\n三藩市領事館庇護嗰條女走咗出嚟已被拘捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123404</a><br />\n<br />\n（領導先走）中国駐侯斯頓領事館關門！美方強破門 撤下五星旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區今日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123707</a><br />\n<br />\n突發！10名支那人偷渡入長洲被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123136</a><br />\n<br />\n[伊朗戰線] 成功connect 伊朗人 (圖片文宣要人)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123567</a><br />\n<br />\n香港真喺玩完 有元朗街坊見到大陸人一路行街一路播毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121428</a><br />\n<br />\n我係船員代理，有嘢想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118934</a><br />\n<br />\n立場： 調查後發現中聯辦買入全棟樂怡軒同蒲飛路 18 號 並擁有選民登記<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAdhPNU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAdhPNU</a>"},{"pid":"13ea4fb972418e4920d1db4e8b29727607f05d97","tid":2125093,"uid":38216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:47:18.000Z","msg":"益咗你啦，唔識寶"},{"pid":"b513cf3583a5a0d1651a62011ecca503ba9a3138","tid":2125093,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69dca2ed6d71b3b9bfa833af267546c04f80d95","tid":2125093,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20200726/bkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcommentary%2F20200726%2Fbkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=796914bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/commentary/20200726/bkn-20200726000346848-0726_00832_001.html</a><br />\n世界各地的<span class=\"red\">新冠肺炎</span>疫情至今未有受控迹象，內地雖然抗疫成績領先，但好了傷疤忘了痛的死性不改。最先爆發疫情的湖北武漢，餐飲業依然亂象叢生。有當地民眾從食店外賣豬肚湯回家，竟駭然發現是蝙蝠湯，掛羊頭賣狗肉，監管當局卻置若罔聞，一旦病從口入，疫情再起，該當何罪？<br />\n<br />\n武漢陳先生近日在某食店買了一煲豬肚湯回家，連續喝到第三日才發現湯內有一隻完整的蝙蝠，嚇得一家人趕緊去做病毒核酸檢測，幸未驗出病毒。陳先生隨即往食店理論，惟對方卻指自己只是分銷商，熬製工序是生產商的事；生產商則稱熬湯過程費時，若是己方所為，蝙蝠早應被煮爛，反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去，結果成了各有各說，不知該相信誰。<br />\n<br />\n正如當地市場監管部門事後檢查指出，相關食店的衞生及生產環節俱無發現問題，又表示涉事生產商在當地已經營多年，過往檢查亦未發現有甚麼不合規情況，看來欲知真相，惟有去問蝙蝠，那又要市監作甚？好在食店的老闆比較有「人情味」，表示願向客人支付一定精神補償及相關核酸檢測費用，估計事件至此已是最「圓滿」的結局，否則再糾纏下去，食客有無精力奉陪已是疑問，搞不好還會上演事件「反轉」，豈非自找麻煩？<br />\n<br />\n不可不知，武漢市早前爆發奪命新冠肺炎疫情，搞得人心惶惶，病毒源頭就被高度懷疑來自蝙蝠等野生動物，如今更被拿來煲湯，不叫人害怕才怪。莫說是蝙蝠，就算吃到老鼠、蟑螂、蒼蠅也不能容忍，問題更非像<span class=\"red\">非洲豬瘟</span>病死豬肉那樣，強調煮熟吃就沒事了，顧客吃了「加料」食物，一句檢疫正常、身體健康又能代表甚麼？保障餐飲業乃至整個食品行業的安全衞生是民生大事，更是政府不可推卸的責任，不能每次都語焉不詳，不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n民以食為天，食以安為先。可惜內地餐飲業衞生安全問題總是爆完又爆，沒完沒了，民眾更別指望可以食得安心。而且每次發生類似的問題，地方監管部門似乎都已形成了一套嫺熟的應對措施，不是說食肆衞生檢查正常，就是以源頭無法追查搪塞，再來就像江蘇南京江寧區市監人員那樣，在處理高速公路服務區餐廳吃到蛆蟲投訴時，任由餐廳經理當面吃掉蛆蟲毀證，令人瞠目結舌。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，更多的食安問題不是由食客主動檢舉揭發，就是由媒體記者深入虎穴做臥底，探查取證踢爆，所有監管部門都彷彿成了擺設，箇中原由不問可知。想必平時都被打點好了，層層包庇，食安亂象豈能不是層出不窮！<br />\n<br />\n良心店！買豬肚送蝙蝠咁蝕底嘅嘢都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔畀人叫武漢肺炎但叫人哋非洲豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa970a1af172623dc8bea53f1dde808f006d2417","tid":2125093,"uid":60651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7cad0322af86c7ed6c6222f2d6b8b78a67695d0","tid":2125093,"uid":81273,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"反質疑食客是否在喝湯時不小心讓蝙蝠飛了進去<br />\n講完自己有冇笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"奇蹟之插入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d914c277232eb5c9f52b2f35a3149f2298bc475a","tid":2125093,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497de4fcacda06fa707bf6ef47f48e28248eeba6","tid":2125093,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"點解支那人咁鍾情蝙蝠?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:10:54.000Z","msg":"邊有咁撚多豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547b118bd74892ce360c657bd3a1b10df1ec0cf9","tid":2125093,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:17:30.000Z","msg":"間野應該都有賣蝙蝠湯, 落錯料<br />\n<br />\n間中我食河粉都有幾條米粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6f79475870bd93dba209bafecfbf7ee676980d","tid":2125093,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"借位，睇下連登被沉底既熱門post:<br />\n<br />\n三藩市領事館庇護嗰條女走咗出嚟已被拘捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123404</a><br />\n<br />\n（領導先走）中国駐侯斯頓領事館關門！美方強破門 撤下五星旗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區今日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123707</a><br />\n<br />\n突發！10名支那人偷渡入長洲被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123136</a><br />\n<br />\n[伊朗戰線] 成功connect 伊朗人 (圖片文宣要人)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123567</a><br />\n<br />\n香港真喺玩完 有元朗街坊見